etc.. is added. This is mainly because with IRC, you are working with many
strings, and you have to parse each, perform actions on certain events,
etc. It gets very slow after a while. We have already resorted to ASM,
and now there are more lines of ASM than Blitz code! (nearly ;)).. And
theres a lot of blitz code :)
Blitz strings are EXTREMELY SLOW!.. There was a routine we wrote for
parsing colour and softstyle codes which was 200 times (yes 200 TIMES!)
faster when I finally converted it to ASM.

